original: FOGELBERG, Svenoscar, Direktör, Stockholm, f Gävle 7/6 11, gm Ingrid Norman. Fader: Dir Birger Fogelberg. Vkst dir f Tekn AB Flora (Florodol), Gävle. Styr.ordf i AB Choklad- & Konfektfabr Freja, Gävle. Resor: Norge, Danm, Tyskl, Holl, Belg, Engl, Amer, Frankr, Span, Schweiz, Italien, Ungern. Hobby: Motorsport.
translated:
FOGELBERG, Svenoscar, Director, Stockholm, born in Gävle on June 7th, 1911, married to Ingrid Norman. Father: Director Birger Fogelberg. Was a managing director at Tekn AB Flora (Florodol) in Gävle. Chairman of the board at AB Choklad- & Konfektfabr Freja in Gävle. Traveled to Norway, Denmark, Germany, the Netherlands, Belgium, England, America, France, Spain, Switzerland, Italy, and Hungary. Hobby: Motorsport.

Note: '\d\d m. partners name' indicates that the person got married in the year 19xx.
